    "description": {
      "value": "<h2>Description</h2>\n<p>Like a hat of disguise, this garment allows its wearer to alter her appearance. It functions as an alter self spell (as opposed to disguise self). The hat becomes a part of the disguise and can be a hat, a helmet, a headscarf, and so forth.</p>\n<p><strong>Base Item:</strong></p>\n<h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3>\n<p>Craft Wondrous Item, alter self</p>\n<h3><strong>Source: </strong></h3>\n<p>Curse of the Riven Sky</p>\n<p><strong>Foundry Usage:</strong></p>\n<p>To apply affects from this item, use the Alter Self buffs in the compendium.<br /></p>",
